The user's home share\-fs partition.
.IP
file://<path>/[<filename>]
.IP
An absolute local hard\-drive path.
.IP
<app>[:<group>][@<host>[:<port>]]:/<path>/[<filename>]
.IP
An absoluate path in a share\-fs partition.
